t Managers focused on retention and growth revenueManage, Hire, and Lead performance conversations with team membersHave experience navigating complex deal cycles across a technical portfolio of products Effectively expand Cloudinary's customer footprintParticipate in virtual and onsite meetings with strategic clients and partnersAccurately forecast growth and retention opportunitiesEscalate customer questions and issues to the appropriate teams    About You:  Minimum of 4+ years of experience in a customer-facing, B2B, revenue-generating leadership role in Saas/technology space 7+ years of experience in software account management and/or sales requiredStrong presentation skills, executive presence, and influencing skills History of exceeding sales goals Highly motivated as well as able to develop a highly motivated and success-oriented teamProven ability to integrate knowledge across disciplines to include relationship management, consultative selling, closing contracts, operation/process flow, and product functionWillingness to travel    Cloudinary is proud to be an equal opportunity employer dedicated to pursuing a diverse workforce.  \"We are dedicated to fostering an environment of transparency and equity in our hiring practices. In alignment with these values, we are pleased to provide a salary range for our positions based in the United States of America. The salary range for this role is based on the location where you reside. We firmly believe that every candidate's skills, experience, and contributions are valuable, and it's our commitment to compensate accordingly. By sharing this information upfront, we aim to ensure that all candidates understand the base salary numbers associated with this position from the outset. We encourage open dialogue and transparency throughout the hiring process, and we are eager to discuss further during the interview stages. We aim to build a team where each member feels valued and fairly compensated for their contributions. Thank you for considering joining our team, and we look forward to the possibility of working together.\"              Show more                Show less",
