        "value": "5135c593-0843-41d9-8cb9-011fbd46b4e2"
    },
    "description": "Cloudinary was founded in 2012 to solve a simple problem: making it an easy platform to manage images & videos. Over the years we evolved into a $120 million+ annual recurring revenue business serving 10,000 companies across industries – from the smallest Shopify stores to iconic brands like Nike and other worldwide companies.  Cloudinary is now the foundational technology for all images and videos on the internet. Only we provide robust, flexible, and intelligent solutions for every business in the world to harness the power of visual media to tell its story. As a single source of truth for brands’ image and video needs, we also provide a comprehensive array of APIs and integrations to transform every brand into a masterful visual storyteller.  If images and video are the electricity powering the new digital world, Cloudinary is the power grid: enabling anyone to easily plug in and “light up” their business with high-impact visual media, without worrying about the science behind the electrical current.  Cloudinary Labs aims to drive innovation by executing projects and product PoCs through rapid prototyping and market understanding. We’re looking for someone who wants to build great new things and lead others who want to do the same. As the Labs Lead, you will function as a product visionary with an entrepreneurial mindset, leading a small, nimble team in executing ideas, launching projects, and validating them with the market.   Key Responsibilities:     Lead a small, agile team through development and validation phases, fostering a culture of adaptability, excellence, innovation, high performance, and continuous improvement  Serve as hands-on product lead, managing all product and project-related aspects from idea to launch  Translate vision into optimal product PoCs that effectively validate hypotheses, ensuring they are actionable and aligned with predefined objectives and KPIs  Drive the Labs project's success across various stages, including strategic direction, operational execution, market penetration, and project performance  Create and maintain an ideation pipeline, tracking new market dynamics and transformative technologies to understand their potential impact on Cloudinary  Define and execute go-to-market launch activities, optimizing market reach and potential  Gather design partners, customers, and market feedback to understand the potential impact and market fit  Guide strategic decisions and graduation phases of product PoCs  Champion Labs and outputs both internally and externally. Fosters cross-functional collaboration with departmental stakeholders and Cloudinary's function heads, getting mindshare, building confidence, and inspiring change  Develop and implement innovative methodologies, playbooks and repeatable processes       About you:     Curious and excited by emerging technologies, new market dynamics, and unserved opportunities  Proven track record in entrepreneurial leadership, with versatile experience in the initial stages of startups, including product development, go-to-market strategy, marketing, and sales  +7 years experience as a Product Manager with end-to-end responsibilities for a SaaS product (preferably API-based)  Strategic risk-taker with foresight to create a compelling (yet grounded) product vision, and iteratively executing on it  Strong people manager with the ability to guide teams through ambiguity, spark creativity, and help them grow in changing environments and strive for excellence  Strong presentation and communication skills, both verbally and in writing   Vast experience in leading customer-facing engagements  MBA is a plus      Cloudinary is proud to be an equal opportunity employer dedicated to pursuing a diverse workforce.  ",
