 servicesExcellent communication and interpersonal skills, with the ability to effectively present technical information to both technical and non-technical audiencesAbility to work independently and as part of a team in a fast-paced environmentWillingness to travel for client meetings and industry events    Why Join Cloudinary:  Opportunity to work with cutting-edge technology and industry-leading clientsA collaborative and inclusive work culture that values creativity, innovation, and diversityCompetitive compensation package with performance-based incentivesFlexible remote work options and opportunities for career advancement and professional development    \"We are dedicated to fostering an environment of transparency and equity in our hiring practices. In alignment with these values, we are pleased to provide a salary range for our positions based in the United States of America. The OTE range for this role is based on the location where you reside. We firmly believe that every candidate's skills, experience, and contributions are valuable, and it's our commitment to compensate accordingly. By sharing this information upfront, we aim to ensure that all candidates understand the base salary numbers associated with this position from the outset. We encourage open dialogue and transparency throughout the hiring process, and we are eager to discuss further during the interview stages. We aim to build a team where each member feels valued and fairly compensated for their contributions. Thank you for considering joining our team, and we look forward to the possibility of working together.\"              Show more                Show less",
    "employmentType": "Full-time"
}

