    },
    "description": "We are looking for an experienced, technology-oriented sales development representative to join Cloudinary’s SDR team to support enterprise sales. This candidate should be an enthusiastic sales professional with an entrepreneurial mindset to develop their territory through thoughtful, multi-channel outreach. If you are career driven and have a track record of success, this could be your perfect opportunity to launch into tech sales!   Responsibilities:     Identify and set Outbound meetings that convert to qualified opportunities in the sales pipeline  Partner with their AE to determine the strategy for assigned target accounts in the region  Collaborate with Marketing to work on Account Based campaigns and field events  Have a deep understanding of the current customer business and how Cloudinary can help to expand its footprint  Meet and exceed minimum KPIs on a daily basis  Achieve or exceed the monthly quota of Qualified Opportunities and Meetings Held  Conduct high-level strategy discussions with Senior Executives in Target and Prospect Accounts Research and build new and existing accounts (i.e. adding contacts, sending regular emails, coordinating strategic discovery meetings)  Train on Cloudinary’s products, use cases and customer case studies to better understand the platform and be able to effectively pitch to prospects       About you:     2+ Years of overall experience and at least 1 year in sales are required  Experience in cold calling, managing a list of target accounts, and identifying prospects   Proven track record of exceeding targets and quota in an Enterprise + Outbound environment  Experience working with Salesforce, Outreach.io, and LinkedIn Sales Navigator, Zoominfo, Lusha, and Orum or similar tools      ",
