ityCompetitive compensation package with performance-based incentivesFlexible remote work options and opportunities for career advancement and professional development    If you are passionate about helping clients succeed in the digital world and thrive in a fast-paced, innovative environment, we want to hear from you! Apply now to join our team as a Cloudinary Account Manager.  \"We are dedicated to fostering an environment of transparency and equity in our hiring practices. In alignment with these values, we are pleased to provide an OTE range for our positions based in the United States of America. The salary range for this role is based on the location where you reside.  We firmly believe that every candidate's skills, experience, and contributions are valuable, and it's our commitment to compensate accordingly. By sharing this information upfront, we aim to ensure that all candidates understand the base salary numbers associated with this position from the outset.  We encourage open dialogue and transparency throughout the hiring process, and we are eager to discuss further during the interview stages. We aim to build a team where each member feels valued and fairly compensated for their contributions. Thank you for considering joining our team, and we look forward to the possibility of working together.\"              Show more                Show less",
    "employmentType": "Full-time"
}

