clude product management experience)   5+ years experience in the video space preferred   Must have experience with SaaS  Excellent writing and presentation skills  Experience with multiple business buyer personas, including technical buyers  Proven creativity and messaging skills  Highly analytical, data-driven approach  Comfortable with both high-level strategy and hands-on work    ",
