    "description": " Job Description   As a Senior Analyst, you will lead and support various delivery services provided by the Managed Services team to our customers. This will include overseeing and performing claims processing, contract maintenance, formulary and data validation, data management, report generation, trend insights, customer interaction and support, and documentation for Managed Care, Medicaid, Tricare, and Part D rebates. You can expand your talents to take lead roles on outsourcing initiatives and contribute to IntegriChain’s project methodologies, engagement strategies, and industry solutions. As a Senior Analyst, you will be accountable for the following:  Setup and maintenance of customer contracts and membership within the rebate system  Lead and perform the processing of claims that support a variety of business processes for a large base of pharmaceutical manufacturers  Formulary and script level validation  Analyze rebate calculations for consistency and accuracy, research variances, and resolve disputes and issues  Analyze and provide trend insights  Execute various reporting activities required for customer compliance  Support ongoing customer relationships  Identify and assist in process and system improvements  Participate and collaborate on ad hoc projects  Subject matter expert of either/both Medicaid or Managed Care rebates",
