    "description": " Company Description    Vibracoustic is a global automotive NVH expert that provides customized solutions to enhance comfort, efficiency, safety, and durability in vehicles. With around 12,000 employees at 40 locations across 17 countries, Vibracoustic serves major automotive manufacturers, offering solutions across all automotive segments. The company recorded total sales of 2.7 billion € in 2023.    Role Description    This is a full-time on-site role for a Product Costing Engineer at Vibracoustic in Noida. The Product Costing Engineer will be responsible for day-to-day tasks related to costing analysis, cost optimization, and cost management for automotive products. The role involves collaborating with cross-functional teams to analyze product costs, identify cost-saving opportunities, and ensure pricing competitiveness.    Qualifications     Cost Analysis, Cost Optimization, and Cost Management skills  Experience in automotive industry product costing  Ability to collaborate with cross-functional teams  Data analysis and problem-solving skills  Proficiency in MS Excel and cost estimation tools  Bachelor's degree in Engineering, Finance, or related field  Strong attention to detail and organizational skills  Knowledge of automotive manufacturing processes is a plus  ",
