    "description": "Vibracoustic is part of the Freudenberg Group. The company ensures a smooth and quiet ride experience in every vehicle. We are driven by our purpose of adding comfort to mobility and providing the perfect solution for the NVH challenges of our automotive customers. As a leading supplier, Vibracoustic is the right place for open-minded, ambitious team-players with a hands-on mentality. Our innovative, safe and dynamic working atmosphere offers many opportunities for your personal growth and development in a global network. Want to join the team?   Mohali  On-Site   Vibracoustic India Pvt. Ltd.  You support our team as    Deputy Manager Supplier Quality Assurance (SQA)     Responsibilities      Ensure ok product's from supplier at plant works.  Responsible for Supplier Feasibility, SPM supplier initial parts layout, testing, line trials, Supplier ELV as per requirements, supplier new mold layout, testing, approval process, ECR/ECN in New products/ Running products related to child parts.  Supplier PPAP activities aligned with APQP timeline plan.  Suppler Audit as per Plan Vs Actual- aligned to on-time closure and verification of the same.  Supplier PTR  Verification and information flow to concerned supplier partners of daily quality issues at Incoming/In process/Final Inspection.  Responsible for on-time containment actions implementation at Inhouse- transit- supplier end.  On-time resolution with the supplier partners for complaints.  Alignment of receipt material along with Supplier PDIR as well as RMTC along with every batch and for arranging RMTC & PDIR along with every supplies from the suppliers.     Qualifications      Bachelor of Mechanical  7.5 years   Hindi, English.     Some of your Benefits     Cafeteria/ Canteen:  We offer fresh food on-site, both hot and cold.   Diversity & Inclusion:  We focus on providing an inclusive environment and recognize our diversity contributes to our success.   Easily Reachable:  Easy, low-stress access by